title: [Sevannha's Outfitting]
[Sevannha's Magic Shoppe]
[Sevannha's General Store]
description: Beneath an elegantly arched fel ceiling, an old elven war banner hangs on one of the red brocade walls.  A carved oak table and an elegantly carved oak armoire sit in opposite corners while a pile of unmarked crates rests on a glossy black ebonwood floor.
